                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2001-07-21</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>This book will help any who are struggling with finding authentic work, or the transformation of current work. The kind of wisdom on action Palmer describes here can help us all to find and to engage in work and creativity which serves simplicity, mindfulness and healing rather than materialism and distraction.</span>
                  
              
